  "description": "<p>🔥 Events Marketing Crew (Entry-Level)</p><p>Looking for a role that gets you out, active, and learning fast?</p><p>Join our team supporting brands through events, roadshows & live activations 🎉</p><p>What You’ll Do 🎯</p><p>• Represent brands at events & outreach locations 🏷️</p><p>• Engage customers face-to-face and explain promotions 💬</p><p>• Support daily campaign executions ⚙️</p><p>What You’ll Get 🚀</p><p>• On-the-job training & mentorship 🌱</p><p>• Build confidence, communication & people skills 💪</p><p>• Exposure to different brands and campaigns 🌐</p><p>• Growth opportunities based on performance 📈</p><p>Who This Is For ⭐</p><p>• Students / fresh grads / ORD / first-job seekers 🎓</p><p>• Comfortable talking to people</p><p>• Willing to learn — no experience needed</p><p>📩 Apply now — shortlisted candidates will be contacted!</p>",
